{"tid":1565510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"！！！勿墜分化陷阱！！！","createTime":"2019-09-13T07:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T09:02:59.000Z","uid":21715,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cde1127d8a37d13a989cd4f0519e2271ebfc955b","tid":1565510,"uid":21715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:31:36.000Z","msg":"呢兩日已經有好多post 開始吹<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>分化風</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n包括但不限於：<br />\n<br />\n1. 集會唱歌有撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 有和理非上大台講話，多得和理非先有今日，勇武係垃圾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 跳閘有撚用，比人拉抵撚死，跳得閘又咪係貪錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">手足緊記</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不分化，不割席<br />\n<br />\n連登已經被滲透，大家見一個0.5 block 一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要對付分化撚最好嘅手段係：<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔撚理佢，唔撚覆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 覆佢屌鳩佢，但記得用不推文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 完全封鎖，耳根清靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">見到有好多手足忍唔住口屌啲分化撚，咁樣反而係幫助緊佢地散播分化資訊！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">推上去比更多人見到</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c86c761de69d08bc86abcc0fd1af6d3350b855a","tid":1565510,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:32:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QfFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=41f1d99c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區集合地點!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n油麻地、佐敦、尖沙咀: 梳士巴利公園(太空館附近)<br />\n荃灣、大窩口、青衣: 荃灣公園(海濱長廊)、青衣海濱長廊<br />\n葵興、葵芳、荔景: 林士德遊樂場、葵涌運動場<br />\n美孚: 嶺南之風<br />\n太子、旺角: 花墟公園<br />\n荔枝角、長沙灣: 長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗: 通州街公園<br />\n油塘、藍田: 油塘道遊樂場<br />\n將軍澳、寶琳、坑口、康城<br />\n中西區（西區、中環、金鐘、半山、山頂）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"5bb635021654556b939c37cfeb43c0c26b11adfa","tid":1565510,"uid":281342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2BA5TGe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2BA5TGe.jpg&h=a22beac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K1yCKNU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK1yCKNU.jpg&h=1a555185&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3bQhKNV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3bQhKNV.jpg&h=422c053f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1cenbsV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cenbsV.png&h=90e5d8ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RKYSyGf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRKYSyGf.jpg&h=2f3a27f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc9aacd670ee67061867e2af16630b0df